      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont wanna call my doctor right now, they're always so dismissive and it takes forever to get an appointment. if i just stay hydrated and maybe take a little less of it for a day or two to see if the tremors stop, would that be okay? like, is there a way i can just manage this at home for a bit so i don't have to deal with the hassle of the clinic?",
